  "instructions": "Study these words. Notice how many verbs belong to Group 1 and end in the 'U' sound before masu (e.g. Suimasu, Tsukaimasu, Torimasu). These will all conjugate to the double 'tte' in the Te-form.",
  "contentItems": [
    {
      "type": "introduction",
      "text": "Mentally practice converting these verbs to the Te-form as you read them. Hairimasu -> Haitte. Torimasu -> Totte."
    }
  ],
